-- Russian cbank cuts forex repo rate to LIBOR plus 0.5 pct
-- 
-- Thu Dec 04, 2014 01:47AM EST
-- None



MOSCOW, Dec 4 (Reuters) - The Russian Central Bank said on Thursday that it had set the foreign currency repo rate at LIBOR plus 0.5 percentage points from Dec.4, down from LIBOR plus 1.5 percentage points last month, to stabilise the currency market.

